title: Federal Aid to States
name: federal-aid-to-states
notes: The Federal Aid to States presents data on federal government aid to state and local governments by state and U.S. Outlying Area.  In this report, grants to state and local governments represent actual expenditures of the federal government, and only grants to state and local governments are included.
